text.tspan: He is a 19 year old undergraduate student at UT Austin. Adam relies heavily on technology
to get his day-to-day tasks done. He takes public transport, mainly bus, to travel around the
city. When he has free time and likes to explore. He is connected to several student clubs.
Adam has huge academic workload for some parts of the semester when he dedicates all of
his time to his studies. In his free time, he likes to socialize and do fun activities.
